         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">23/9/82 ¶  ¶ The few algs, concerning which I wrote you a few days ago, ¶  dear Mr Ramsay, as sent by you some months ago for naming came from  ¶ Bondi ¶ . I am deeply grieved at the Losses of your L....</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">82.09.23b</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Edward Ramsay</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">ML MSS.562, Letters to E. P. Ramsay 1862-91, Mitchell Library, State Library of New South Wales, Sydney.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">23/9/82</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The few algs, concerning which I wrote you a few days ago,<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See M to E. Ramsay, 22 September 1882?</p>
               </note> dear Mr Ramsay, as sent by you some months ago for naming came from <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Bondi</hi>
               </seg>. I am deeply grieved at the Losses of your L. S.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">The entire library of the Linnean Society of NSW was lost in the fire that in the early morning of 22 September 1882 destroyed Sydney's Garden Palace, built in the Domain to house the International Exhibition of 1879.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Regardfully</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
         </div>
